chive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_36">36</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_37">37</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_38">38</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_39">39</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_40">40</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_41">41</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_42">42</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_43">43</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_44" class="active">44</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_45">45</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_46">46</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_47">47</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_48">48</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_49">49</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_50">50</a> <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210802231224/http://catholicbible.online/side_by_side/OT/Isa/ch_51">51-66</a> 				</div>
